Paper: hep-th/0007174

Date: 2000-07-21

Title: Boundaries, crosscaps and simple currents

Authors: J. Fuchs, L.R. Huiszoon, A.N. Schellekens, C. Schweigert, J. Walcher

Comments: 11 pages, LaTeX2e, reference added, typos corrected

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B495 (2000) 427-434

Universal formulas for the boundary and crosscap coefficients are presented,which are valid for all symmetric simple current modifications of the chargeconjugation invariant of any rational conformal field theory.